OL,5, A new health and social care tax will  
OL,6, be introduced across the UK to pay for 
OL,7, reforms to the care sector and NHS     
OL,8, funding in England.                    
OL,10,FBoris Johnson said it would raise #12bn
OL,11,Fa year, designed to tackle the health  
OL,12,Fbacklog caused by the Covid pandemic   
OL,13,Fand to bolster social care.            
OL,15,FHe accepted the tax broke a manifesto  
OL,16,Fpledge, but said the "global pandemic  
OL,17,Fwas in no-one's manifesto".            
OL,19,FHowever, Labour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,20,Fsaid the plan was a "sticking plaster".
